{"id": 2053, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，你在游戏里满足感最高的时刻是什么？", "description": "Carry 全场什么的交给别人吧，我只要能安安静静地捡垃圾就好了。", "record_count": 1727, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171207154201SEk29sQaDLoCjIMe.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-11T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 253953, "content": "选择辅助角色进行游戏时，为团队所做的贡献得到队友的感激和赞赏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211109}, {"id": 253698, "content": "lovelive贸然全连", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668570}, {"id": 253699, "content": "不管怎么送，队友都能带你赢，自己躺着就好了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1209978}, {"id": 253958, "content": "中队模式，五人零输出吃鸡", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984924}, {"id": 253704, "content": "全场逆风，最后靠着一己之力完成翻盘", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747223}, {"id": 253960, "content": "686打爆一切", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898852}, {"id": 253705, "content": "全队发挥都不好，但是团结一致实力翻盘一起对对面喷子亮图标。", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930436}, {"id": 253961, "content": "脚下的透明逐渐变冷的时候，云的僧侣正站在我身后。他能从海水的咸味预知十年后的气象。如果十年后的此刻风推云走，艳阳遍照，他就说，别醒来！如果浓阴恶雨，沙尘飞漫，他就说，到帽子里去。 \n云的僧侣在加速变冷的空气里命令我，到帽子里去。然后，他说出一个不后悔的事。我们都在一起了。我们都在", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037207}, {"id": 253706, "content": "杰洛特捡垃圾", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1209998}, {"id": 253962, "content": "抽到SSR算什么。抽到UR才爽", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1209656}, {"id": 254730, "content": "没看攻略却发现隐藏彩蛋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1214715}, {"id": 253707, "content": "遇到团结一致的队友", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599206}, {"id": 253708, "content": "就是不以通关或者任务为目的，自己想干啥就干啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1175374}, {"id": 254477, "content": "没有充钱拿到了限定装备", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1062444}, {"id": 253710, "content": "你们厉害牛逼各种姿势，我默默捡装备猥琐发育……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050177}, {"id": 259086, "content": "挨毒吃包，圈外第八", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236558}, {"id": 253711, "content": "大概是打完一把比赛的时候大家商业胡吹?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591280}, {"id": 253714, "content": "带飞一群菜鸟，边游走输出边语音指挥。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1139257}, {"id": 254227, "content": "全场carry并且夺得全场最佳", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488852}, {"id": 257300, "content": "极限反杀 极限翻盘", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1121755}, {"id": 253717, "content": "崩坏3一发入魂的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165969}, {"id": 253719, "content": "一口气通关", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210039}, {"id": 253720, "content": "解开谜题的一瞬间，绝对高潮，成就感爆表", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 459529}, {"id": 254744, "content": "p社五萌打赢要对方割地赔款时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242684}, {"id": 256024, "content": "一直连胜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190328}, {"id": 253721, "content": "养成类游戏毕业", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993360}, {"id": 253723, "content": "俄罗斯方块40000分，一条100分", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208095}, {"id": 253724, "content": "逆风翻盘", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210051}, {"id": 253728, "content": "卡关好久终于完美通关的时候(๑•̀ㅂ•́)و✧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 195734}, {"id": 253730, "content": "回家好好聚聚", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1180245}, {"id": 253732, "content": "敌人的雪条持续减少的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1027278}, {"id": 258341, "content": "智商压制", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673577}, {"id": 253734, "content": "对面从头到尾没碰到我，我把他玩死了！！！?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 965526}, {"id": 274215, "content": "打到游戏里只剩下我一个人，完全没人玩了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1303540}, {"id": 253735, "content": "第一赛季单排上枪神", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210081}, {"id": 253737, "content": "残血反杀！！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1196870}, {"id": 253738, "content": "白金？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480571}, {"id": 257835, "content": "发现了新奇有趣的套路（不一定有利于胜利或通关）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1163282}, {"id": 253740, "content": "赢", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210107}, {"id": 254252, "content": "搜到大死鱼，用哥布林狂抢70W金币", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211810}, {"id": 253741, "content": "实况用中国狂胜棒子", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403859}, {"id": 253743, "content": "炉石传说开局天胡", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156636}, {"id": 254000, "content": "全队完美配合吊打对面然后发开心的表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211001}, {"id": 253745, "content": "玩辅助开大献祭自己队友赢团战", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594200}, {"id": 253746, "content": "抽到SSR", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210114}, {"id": 253747, "content": "通关一个自己喜欢的游戏，看到了故事结局", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1128176}, {"id": 253748, "content": "在COQ当了一年多的联盟主，每当我的身体力行得到各国队友的称赞，说\"You're a good leader\"、“I love my alliance”时我都满足感爆棚！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461690}, {"id": 253749, "content": "熬到自己所在区的人都不玩了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042608}, {"id": 255286, "content": "七杀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217939}, {"id": 253752, "content": "战争雷霆都快输了，和仅剩的几个队友抗住了对面所有人，一波反杀成功胜利", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273908}]}